<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>yé sū yǔ wǒ tóng zài 迦南306</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 yé sū yǔ wǒ tóng zài, wǒ hái pà shén me! bù wèi bī pò jiān xīn kǎn kě.
 huàn nán lǐ yǒu ēn diǎn, kǔ sè zhōng yǒu xǐ lè, fēng fēng yǔ yǔ dōu shì gē. shén me
 lì liàng ràng wǒ men xīn hé yī gòng qiú suǒ?
 shì shén me xī yǐn běn lái mò shēng de nǐ hé wǒ?
 dōu míng bái, bù bì shuō, fēi shān dù shuǐ zǒu biàn měi gè jiǎo luò.
 jǔ qǐ shǒu, zài qǐ shì, bù mián zhī yè tóng dù guò.
 dōu míng bái, bù bì shuō, bèi qiú zhī gē dōu chàng guò.
 jǔ qǐ shǒu, zài qǐ shì, hái yào xiàng qián bù yào pà shén me.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>306</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
</song>